{
  "stem": "14463.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was three months in [? gimps. ?] And I'll never forget the time because, you know, it was itching like mad.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, on the-- on the bottom , it was itchy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I couldn't scratch it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my mother put a-- you know, on the window sill, she put some covers, you know, from the bed so it would be soft.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I could sit on that and look downstairs and say hello to my friends [LAUGHS] when they were passing by.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So the school was a happy school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I would say 90% were Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So that was from 8 o'clock to 12:00, 12:30.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Then I came home, and that's where my father was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He shut the shop every day and came home for lunch when I and my brother came home from school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we were having every day a warm lunch together with my parents, my mother, my father every day, and this was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I loved it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE] never had a time, but my father always had the time for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so-- and that was [INAUDIBLE] something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Then I went-- and this was contrary to any thing which a boy would do in a Hasidic home-- across the street, not far away, there was a [? polana. ?] You know, it was a big ground.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I used to play soccer on there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was contrary to anything, you know, and I did it quietly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father knew about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother knew about it but they didn't talk about it, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to play soccer on there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I used to run home quickly, and have a bit of a wash, change, whatever, and went to the cheder.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
